links.title: From the Presidents Desk
links.content:
Aluminum Coil Anodizing Corporation
501 E. Lake Street · Streamwood, IL 60107
630-837-4000 · HR FAX: 866-729-9747
www.acacorp.com
Thank you for visiting our acacorp.com website. If you’ve visited us before, you will
notice a new look as we have redesigned our site in order to give you more information
about our company, our employees, the products we offer, and the markets we serve.
Aluminum Coil Anodizing Corp. (ACA) has been in the business of anodizing aluminum
coils since 1961. We are located near Chicago in Streamwood, Illinois. In addition to
anodizing, we offer value-added services such as slitting, shearing, embossing,
degreasing, etching, bright-dipping, and anodizing colors. Our capabilities continue to
change as we grow and provide solutions to our customers.
ACA services a variety of industries including, lighting, architectural, automotive, solar,
and other specialty markets. Our sister company Lawrence & Frederick (L&F) services
the nameplate, voice coil, and the rewards and recognition markets.
We invite you to tour our website in depth. If you have any questions, our For Your
Information tab can provide you with frequently asked questions, general information
about anodizing and a point of contact to one of our team members who will be more
than happy to answer any questions that you may have.
We sincerely appreciate your interest in Aluminum Coil Anodizing (ACA) and look
forward to partnering with you in the future.
